{"tid":2043993,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"藍屍spin美國, 咁答就得「人地民選政府要照顧民意, 警察做錯係有法律制裁」","createTime":"2020-05-30T20:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T07:00:52.000Z","uid":123774,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"75115dedc6697af78793d5e2e3bbddcc9f87f93e","tid":2043993,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T20:06:11.000Z","msg":"成件事同香港只有一個共通點 就係有警暴<br />\n<br />\n唔同嘅係人哋<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>民選政府要照顧民意 <br />\n會按法律去制裁黑暴</strong></span><br />\n由當日殺死黑人 到今日開槍鎮壓都係<br />\n人哋警察要為自己行為負責任<br />\n<br />\n唔需要將香港示威同件事扯上其他關係<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BWmydpd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBWmydpd.png&h=b39176bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZL5bKvU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZL5bKvU.png&h=863f50d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kXTQfCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkXTQfCA.jpg&h=9d4e0e11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21e2dd2fca2538a402cf00844f58219f81f48090","tid":2043993,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T20:06:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2e8dbc5ce3b9e8bfa71bedfff87ab70ea97dc9","tid":2043993,"uid":152222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T20:07:46.000Z","msg":"同佢講美國都係學中國<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/gmmj0709/status/1266652479325900800?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgmmj0709%2Fstatus%2F1266652479325900800%3Fs%3D19&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypDzcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=fd37d8f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgmmj0709%2Fstatus%2F1266652479325900800%3Fs%3D19&h=baf044f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/gmmj0709/status/1266652479325900800?s=19</a>"},{"pid":"f64ab34ce21